      "content": "well i tried calling my clinic but they're closed until tomorrow and i feel like i'm getting worse... the pressure in my face is killing me. i checked online and it said ciprofloxacin is a common one for sinus stuff. since i've already taken it before and it worked fine, would it be really bad to just take a couple pills now so i can sleep? and for the sudafed, is there a specific dose that's safe so i dont have to worry?",
