      "content": "i hear you, but an emergency room is just so much hassle and expensive and honestly i feel like it's just a normal sinus thing, not a life or death situation. i just really need relief so i can rest. if i just take one cipro and one sudafed tonight, is there any reason that would actually hurt the baby? like, is there a specific reason it's flagged or is it just a precaution? i just want to know if it's actually dangerous or if everyone just says that to be safe.",
